summary: So I’m watching Journey’s End (Doctor Who S4E14)
body:
So I’m watching Journey’s End (Doctor Who S4E14)

And the Doctor shouts Davros a lot with the occasional Sean Connery-esque ‘sh’ instead of ‘s’.

So I keep hearing “Davrosh” which in turn makes me think of Gavroche from Les Mis and now I want to see and hear Davros singing “Do You Hear the People Sing?” while spinning around.

I'm also a multi-shipper. It's likely I do not sail your ship, but I don't wank and expect visitors to play nicely as well. That includes not adding hate or negativity to my posts, altering them to suit your own ships, or removing my original comments. If you do, you will be blocked.

blog.name: ygrain-synaerasis
blog.title: L'Echappée Belle d' Ygraïn
blog.description:
" Elle voulait une vie d'aventures, une vie folle, une vie plus grande qu'elle.Et l'on disait tout autour d'elle : [Ygraïn] rêve". Timothée de Fombelle, Victoria rêve

Je ne sais pas dessiner, les artworks que vous verrez ici ne sont pas les miens. Mais vous trouverez toujours un lien vers une gallerie de leurs auteurs. Personnellement, je ne fais que des montages (wallpaper, digiscrap, bannière ...) à partir de captures d'écran (screencap).. Ce tumblr est ma gallerie de rêves éphémères, mon échappée belle où je viens me ressourcer, me changer les idées, trouver un support à mes rêveries grâce aux fabuleux arts de d'autres artistes. .
Pour me contacter, en cas de problème: ygrain@gmail.com

Sinon: mon blog de lecture est: https://les-lectures-d-ygrain.tumblr.com/

body:
Thirteenth Doctor

I have been a huge fan of this doctor and I have supported this season against past doc fans yet as this season come to a close i… I don’t know. I realize I don’t have that same affection as I had at the end of 9 or ten, don’t feel angry like with 11 or utterly heartbroken like with 12. I was angry with all others saying how the writing sucked etc etc but now I realize, it is truly lacking. I have religiously seen every episode Sundays at 8 et and looking back nothing stands out except my desire for thasmin. I’m upset with this realization.
